Title: Fingers Only Meat Banquet
Plot: Silas and Nancy's lawyer assist her in getting to California as her custody battle with Jill (Jennifer Jason Leigh) heats up. Meanwhile, Andy's relationship takes an intriguing turn; Shane decides to give it the old college try and enrolls in classes; and Doug is left to fend for himself at his job on Wall Street.
ParentalRatingReason: R16 Drug use,sex scenes and offensive language
